div.p:
It is to be noted: 

1st That the refined copper is a United States
                                        investment;

2nd That United States investments in the nitrate industry
                                        comprise approximately 50% of the present production;



3rd That both these industries provide Chile with the
                                        necessary exchange for the payment of the foreign government
                                        debt;

4th That the copper industry provides approximately
                                        $5,000,000 for service on the foreign obligations of the
                                        Development Corporation;

5th That the copper industry employs approximately 40,000
                                        men and the nitrate industry about 25,000.
